::Shadow Wing::

She flew down to Lunarpine. "Megatron has left.  He went off and 
disappeared in the heavy forest.  I couldn't spot him after a while.  
But he's gone for now."  She transformed into bot mode and hugged 
Lunarpine. "One more battle won. Yeah for our side." She stood there 
in front of him and smiled.  She really cared for this, gruff, tough, 
sometimes harsh wolf that stood infront of her.  She discovered that 
she just couldn't help but like him. Only, it was more than 'like'.  
But she wasn't quite sure how much more than 'like' it was, but she 
thought is was a whole lot more than 'like'.
